title: DGK - BALLIN' HAT - AVAILABLE NOW
description:
DGK doesn't need a hoop to ball, and you won't either if you're wearing this new Balling snapback! It features a basketball texture bill and some very recognizable athletic lettering on the front. Look like an all star while you're watching the all star game this year, this snap hat is most definitely a slam dunk!

DGK wanted our favorite remixer, Manolo, to put his spin on "Parental Advisory". It will be playing exclusively on Hellaclips.com on January 6th,2014. Mark your calendars!
